            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            打工的尽头是创业          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                      棱角talk                                  </span>                                                              <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                棱角talk              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">棱角talk</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">gh_1cb11f123ea0</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">前华为er，科技公司总监。行业认知、管理、思维提升、个人进阶… 围观、合作、咨询&amp;商务：lengjiao0817</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p data-first-child="" data-pid="alv58PQh" style='margin-bottom: 1.4em;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;">这几年大环境不佳，想要稳稳地打工已经变成一件奢侈的事。<span style='outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>在当前国内的环境下，</span>职场人到了一定年纪之后，终将成为职场弃儿。</span></p><p data-first-child="" data-pid="alv58PQh" style='margin-bottom: 1.4em;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;"><span style='outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>因此，</span>很多人调侃说 “宇宙的尽头是体制内<span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;">”</span>，可体制内的岗位毕竟是有限的，这几年频繁出现几百人应聘一个编制岗的情况。未来，体制内的饭碗是否能端的稳吃得香，长远来看，也未必。</span></p><p data-first-child="" data-pid="alv58PQh" style='margin-bottom: 1.4em;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible;">对于大部分人来说，最终都要保持自谋生路的能力。</span><strong style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);outline: 0px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;visibility: visible;">打工的尽头是创业</span></strong><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;visibility: visible;">，当个体户或者做点小生意也算。这方面可以向徽商取取经，今天来聊一聊这个话题。</span></span></p><p data-first-child="" data-pid="alv58PQh" style='margin-bottom: 1.4em;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;'><span style='font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>中国有三大著名商帮：晋商、<span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>潮商<span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>和</span></span>徽商。潮商和晋商在我之前的系列文章里已经有讲到，潮商也就是潮汕商帮，链接附在文末。</span></p><p>徽商最早开始于南宋，发展于元末明初，于明朝中叶形成，在清代中前期处于鼎盛时期，到了清朝中晚期才逐渐衰败，历经六百多年。</p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style='letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(25, 25, 25);font-family: "PingFang SC", Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif;text-align: left;'>徽州位于皖南山区，由于自然灾害频发，食粮短缺，且人口增长迅速，使得徽州人不得不通过经商来谋生。</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: arial;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;">徽商的商业网络遍布全国，主要从事茶叶、丝绸、瓷器等商品贸易。另外，还涉及</span><span style='background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(18, 18, 18);font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "Source Han Sans SC", "Noto Sans CJK SC", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;'>盐、典当和木材等生意。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.034em;">有一些古籍，道出了徽州人经商传统的由来。《徽州府志》记载：“徽州保界山谷，山地依原麓，田瘠确，所产至薄，大都一岁所入，不能支什一。小民多执技艺，或贩负就食他郡者，常十九。”。<span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;">《晋书》记载，徽州人好“离别”，常出外经商。齐梁时，休宁人曹老常往来于江湖间，从事贾贩。</span> 顾炎武也说过：徽州 “中家以下皆无田可业。徽人多商贾，盖势其然也”。 </span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;">看来，自古以来，从商做生意的群体，绝大部分都是由于当地存在严重的生存问题，不得不外出另闯一条路的群体。我在之前文章聊到的闽南商帮、潮汕商帮、温州商帮和晋商，这方面都很类似。尤其在农耕时代，当地适合耕种的土地稀少，在当地也没有太多别的出路<span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;">，生存困难</span>。很多人因此就只能闯出去，<span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;">到其它省份，</span>到海外，渐渐地，就闯出了独特的一条路来。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;box-sizing: content-box;">另外，徽商们往往是官、商一体。<span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>很有名的徽商代表——红顶商人胡雪岩，都与清朝重臣左宗棠有千丝万缕的联系。徽商</span>一旦发迹，热衷于兴院，开学堂，办试馆，培养封建人才，巩固宗法统治。明清时期，徽州就出过很多进士。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;">所以，徽商在很大程度上也属于官商，这点和晋商比较相像，但和现当代的一些商人群体不太一样。当代的一些商人群体，比如温州商帮、闽南商帮和潮汕商帮，很大程度上属于民间游商，主要靠自己寻求出路，其中有很多还是去到海外谋求生存和发展。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>其实，官和商自古就关系紧密，关键在于如何去看待这种现象。只是，有的时期更多的是官营，而有的时期会更多下放私营。</span></span></p><p style='outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style="outline: 0px;box-sizing: content-box;font-size: 17px;">顺便提一下，把视角打开来看，这十来年有几部挺有名的电视剧和纪录片——<span style="outline: 0px;box-sizing: content-box;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">《闯关东》、</span>《走西口》、《下南洋》之类的，都属于当地人出外谋生的无奈之举。闯关东，是山东一带人<span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;">为了</span><span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>逃</span>灾<span style='font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>避</span>难，去到东北地区<span style="outline: 0px;box-sizing: content-box;letter-spacing: 0.578px;">讨生活。走西口，是从<span style='outline: 0px;box-sizing: content-box;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;'>明朝中期到民国初年，山西人、陕西人和河北人背井离乡，打通了中原腹地与蒙古草原的经济和文化通道，谋求生存和发展的一段历史。下南洋，则是东南沿海一带，尤其是潮汕、闽南一带人，去到马来西亚、印尼等南洋地区讨生活的历史。</span></span></span></p><p style='outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style='font-size: 17px;box-sizing: content-box;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>此外，徽文化塑造了徽商的品格 —— 儒商，以儒家文化来指导经商。这方面，很值得现当代的商人群体反思。</span></p><p style='outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: 17px;">回过头来讲，徽商的发展历程，也给了正在寻求出路的人不少启示。</span></p><p data-pid="H81XbslP" style='margin-top: 1.4em;margin-bottom: 1.4em;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style="font-size: 17px;"><span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">在当下如此低迷的<span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">就业环境下，很多人在中年之后，往往都面临着很大的生存挑战。<span style="outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">对于绝大部分人而言，终局都得自寻出路。</span></span></span><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(18, 18, 18);text-align: start;letter-spacing: 0.544px;">就我身边认识的，上了年纪的职场人，有创业的，有做自媒体的，有自己开个小工作室的，有开个小店做点小生意的，有做培训的，有转行做餐饮的，还有不少开网约车的。总之，先存活下来，再谋求发展，天无绝人之路。</span></span><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;'></span></p><p style='outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style='outline: 0px;box-sizing: content-box;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", sans-serif;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;text-indent: 28px;font-size: 17px;'><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5NTE4MzYwNw==&amp;mid=2651907869&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ed8257f6989ced828d007d6870e585bd&amp;chksm=f7b33285c0c4bb932882183eabdf019e0862efb6ea5278f251f1f461e7717536a8e5ca8cd9c0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="中年失业，学学深圳的潮汕帮" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="2" hasload="1" style="outline: 0px;color: var(--weui-LINK);-webkit-user-drag: none;cursor: pointer;">中年失业，学学深圳的潮汕帮</a><br style="outline: 0px;"></span></p><p style='outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5NTE4MzYwNw==&amp;mid=2651908140&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7cd951823a5fee0cc9c66dbee5fb6a8e&amp;chksm=f7b33db4c0c4b4a29046cf7465109a678b074fad32ff8811efa3404ebab03e99ee9ccd25bca6&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="中年困局？了解下闽南商帮" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="2" hasload="1" style="color: var(--weui-LINK);-webkit-user-drag: none;cursor: pointer;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;">中年困局？了解下闽南商帮</span></a></p><p style='outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5NTE4MzYwNw==&amp;mid=2651908198&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0b35badb9002d31f48bec9e337d9d92c&amp;chksm=f7b33dfec0c4b4e8dad94349068ce856a64e91a55564e318be7a16592f2c91c1265fc683aea1&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="大环境下寻求出路，向温州帮取取经" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="2">大环境下寻求出路，向温州帮取取经</a></p><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-id="MzI5NTE4MzYwNw==" data-headimg="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/5AVRMicuYbiar2XTJnEibAFIQia5TKibkmMlPMiaL1FOUU7zicNibPKVefibf