            <title><![CDATA[💬👤 #方方的航空小筑: 🔗 运油20的通用性推测验证之二]]></title>
            <link><![CDATA[http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNjY1MzAzMg==&amp;amp;mid=2247498195&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=14899f810457c2d6cc86236d6d59cf6a&amp;amp;chksm=9a38af02cbabd8f6ed79e466f400ea1b326fe873d3a928beae6c5c4268731a130b6be23d1a44&amp;amp;scene=0&amp;amp;xtrack=1#rd]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            运油20的通用性推测验证之二          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">航空小筑的方方</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                方方的航空小筑              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">方方的航空小筑</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">ffaerofield</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">航迷自留地。非官宣消息都不知道。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p>        去年空军发言人申进科大校曾经说过：</p><p><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100014540" data-ratio="1.8981481481481481" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/BkRwYcxqDH73CYzdnYlULQK1dq7GqibTyUQIOz5bian2CSibo1lnXGyOLDFjjicpvl5bmETT6ZRIpbut25VsNevfGw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1" data-type="jpg" data-w="1080" style="height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;"></p><p>        但是具体如何没见过。</p><p>        这次运油20在运20编队中露了个脸：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100014542" data-ratio="0.5575" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/BkRwYcxqDH7hNsgwonlYjBfJ1ngTxNQ6HWZdR1e2ibwkNTEaKrLCquGTUicCIaedKNIHHTZibB9LHGrhC2aP6SGmQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="2000" style=""></p><p style="text-align: justify;">        单机跟进纵队，第一架领队长机正在向右调整航向。在干啥呢？参见22年的央视八一特别节目：</p><p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100014543" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/BkRwYcxqDH69qibjgxbibEfhVX78iccNtrlFWaHoQPoE96delfb9wBzMBI6zMnLGfLWWUmvBAcfqmia7mrvo2dXx4g/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;"></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100014544" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/BkRwYcxqDH69qibjgxbibEfhVX78iccNtrlFT1wELdma3PaI65wQ7Ad1V5ibOb5Cmbgup6iabzibzkStKAJfJOuwTcDw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style="height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;"></p><p style="text-align: justify;">        运油20参与到这个项目训练，说明该机具备完整的运输空投能力。</p><p style="text-align: justify;">        而且在截图可见，运油20处于编队4号机位置，拍摄机应该是编队5号机。没有任何特殊的地方——比如单独编组什么的。这说明该机的通用性很强，执行运20的常规任务时无需额外处置。</p><p style="text-align: justify;">        这也就是上面说的，一个机队，总体效能相当于两倍的规模。</p><p style="text-align: justify;">        多说几句。忽然间就理解了为啥鹰酱空军一直想要战斗轰炸机，而不是“战斗机黑手党”期望的纯制空战斗机。原因很简单，同样的机群能够执行更多的任务，跟一等人争预算的时候嗓门也更大，为啥不要？至于由此带来的机动性下降的问题，鹰酱原本寄希望于技术的进步来克服——在那个年代就是导弹化。虽然技术局限性和可靠性导致导弹化并不成功，加上米格25的误会催生了第三代能量战斗机，但恰恰也是因为技术进步导致战斗机和战斗轰炸机的分野越来越小，反而在第三代战斗机基础上实现了战斗机和战斗轰炸机合一的梦想，不能不说是一个奇妙的循环。<br></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="2046824393" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
